The paper focuses on transfer learning for image recognition tasks, specifically for medical images of diffuse lung diseases. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper uses deep neural networks, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. The paper also involves visualization methods for analyzing feature representations, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
